script.name: lib.xml.get.data
script.sourceplaintext:
if $a.xmlData @ $lookup.types = [THIS] -> call script lib.xml.getdatatypes : Type='all' @ $int.types = [THIS] -> call script lib.xml.getdatatypes : Type='int' @ $obj.types = [THIS] -> call script lib.xml.getdatatypes : Type='obj'
$node.name = xml get node string: $a.xmlData
$name.type = xml get attribute: data=$a.xmlData, attribute='nametype' if $node.name == 'sector' OR $name.type == 'DATATYPE_SECTOR' $x = xml get attribute: data=$a.xmlData, attribute='name.x' $y = xml get attribute: data=$a.xmlData, attribute='name.y' $name = get sector from universe index: x=$x, y=$y else if $node.name == 'ware' OR $name.type == 'DATATYPE_WARE' $x = xml get attribute: data=$a.xmlData, attribute='name.main' $y = xml get attribute: data=$a.xmlData, attribute='name.sub' $name = get ware from maintype $x and subtype $y else if $node.name == 'race' OR $name.type == 'DATATYPE_RACE' $name = xml get attribute: data=$a.xmlData, attribute='name' skip if $name $name = 0 $name = get race from id=$name else if $obj.types[$node.name] *else if $node.name == 'object' OR $name.type == 'DATATYPE_OBJECT' OR $name.type == 'DATATYPE_SHIP' OR $name.type == 'DATATYPE_STATION' OR $name.type == 'DATATYPE_AGENT' OR $name.type == 'DATATYPE_DEALER' OR $name.type == 'DATATYPE_PASSENGER' OR $name.type == 'DATATYPE_MERCHANT' $name = xml get attribute: data=$a.xmlData, attribute='name' $name = convert serialised string to object: string=$name else $name = xml get attribute: data=$a.xmlData, attribute='name' skip if $name $name = 0 $convert.type = $int.types[$name.type] do if $convert.type $name = change datatype[$name] to $convert.type end
if $node.name == 'table' $return.data = table alloc $children.count = xml get number of children: $a.xmlData $i = 0 while $i < $children.count $child = xml get child: $a.xmlData, id=$i if is datatype[ $child ] == DATATYPE_XMLDATA if xml has attribute: data=$child, attribute='name' $child.name = xml get attribute: data=$child, attribute='name' @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script lib.xml.get.data : XML Data=$child if is datatype[ $ret ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $child.name = $ret[0] $ret = $ret[1] end do if $child.name $return.data[$child.name] = $ret end end inc $i = end $return.data = create new array, arguments=$name, $return.data, null, null, null
else if $node.name == 'array' $array.size = xml get attribute: data=$a.xmlData, attribute='size' $children.count = xml get number of children: $a.xmlData skip if $array.size $array.size = $children.count $return.data = array alloc: size=$array.size $i = 0 while $i < $children.count $child = xml get child: $a.xmlData, id=$i $child.name = xml get attribute: data=$child, attribute='name' @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script lib.xml.get.data : XML Data=$child if is datatype[ $ret ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $child.name = $ret[0] $ret = $ret[1] end do if is datatype[ $child.name ] == DATATYPE_STRING $child.name = string $child.name to integer skip if $child.name $child.name = 0 $return.data[$child.name] = $ret inc $i = end $return.data = create new array, arguments=$name, $return.data, null, null, null
else if xml has attribute: data=$a.xmlData, attribute='type' $datatype = xml get attribute: data=$a.xmlData, attribute='type' if $datatype == 'DATATYPE_SECTOR' $x = xml get attribute: data=$a.xmlData, attribute='data.x' skip if $x $x = 0 $y = xml get attribute: data=$a.xmlData, attribute='data.y' skip if $y $y = 0 $data = get sector from universe index: x=$x, y=$y else if $datatype == 'DATATYPE_INT' $data = xml get attribute: data=$a.xmlData, attribute='data' skip if $data $data = 0 else if $datatype == 'DATATYPE_RACE' $data = xml get attribute: data=$a.xmlData, attribute='data' skip if $data $data = 0 $data = get race from id=$data else if $datatype == 'DATATYPE_WARE' $x = xml get attribute: data=$a.xmlData, attribute='data.main' skip if $x $x = 0 $y = xml get attribute: data=$a.xmlData, attribute='data.sub' skip if $y $y = 0 $data = get ware from maintype $x and subtype $y else if $datatype == 'DATATYPE_OBJECT' OR $datatype == 'DATATYPE_SHIP' OR $datatype == 'DATATYPE_PASSENGER' OR $datatype == 'DATATYPE_AGENT' OR $datatype == 'DATATYPE_STATION' OR $datatype == 'DATATYPE_DEALER' OR $datatype == 'DATATYPE_MERCHANT' $data = xml get attribute: data=$a.xmlData, attribute='data' $data = convert serialised string to object: string=$data
else if $int.types[$datatype] $data = xml get attribute: data=$a.xmlData, attribute='data' skip if $data $data = 0 $type = $int.types[$datatype] $data = change datatype[$data] to $type else $data = xml get attribute: data=$a.xmlData, attribute='data' end $ret = create new array, arguments=$name, $data, null, null, null return $ret end end
end
return $return.data
